videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo drives inside to the basket but Hassan Whiteside is there and extends to block the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (The Greek Freak denied by Whiteside) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: The Greek Freak denied by Whiteside

videos.description: Dwyane Wade enters the game with less than five minutes left in the first quarter and the crowd applauds in excitement.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Wade earns standing ovation entering game) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wade earns standing ovation entering game

videos.description: Dwyane Wade sinks a 3-pointer for his first points in the game in his return to Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Wade scores first points back with the Heat) 2019/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wade scores first points back with the Heat

videos.description: Bam Adebayo doesn't give Giannis Antetokounmpo much room to shoot a basket and he blocks his shot as he goes to score.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Bam not making anything easy for the Greek Freak) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam not making anything easy for the Greek Freak

videos.description: Eric Bledsoe intercepts the ball from Hassan Whiteside and speeds down the court for an easy basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Bledsoe steals and scores) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bledsoe steals and scores

videos.description: Dwyane Wade lobs it up to Hassan Whiteside who finishes with a two-handed jam right at the end of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Wade finds Whiteside for alley-oop slam) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wade finds Whiteside for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Dwyane Wade steals the ball and zooms down the court to score, but Giannis Antetokounmpo elevates to swat the ball away from the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Greek Freak takes on Wade after steal) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Greek Freak takes on Wade after steal

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo intercepts the ball and goes to coast-to-coast but James Johnson beats him there to deny him from getting a bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Greek Freak steal leads nowhere) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Greek Freak steal leads nowhere

videos.description: Khris Middleton shot is denied by Bam Adebayo who rises up for a monster block in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Bam makes cold-hearted rejection) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bam makes cold-hearted rejection

videos.description: With Miami ahead by 4 points, Dwyane Wade shows off his defensive skills and denies Eric Bledsoe from scoring.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Wade's clutch block keeps Miami in front) 2018/02/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wade's clutch block keeps Miami in front
